{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/extras/George_Final.gif?t=1629932324\" /><br>George and Samantha are two adorable pieces of fabric who just happen to be in love (we\u2019ll give you a moment to \u201caww\u201d here). Nothing could keep these two threadly swatches apart - except for an incredibly powerful gust of wind (for most people, it was a light breeze, but that equals hurricane-force winds when you\u2019re fabric) carries Samantha away, leaving George to wonder, Where\u2019s Samantha?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/extras/frank_2.gif?t=1629932324\" /><br>Many obstacles await George on his search for Samantha. Help George overcome puzzles of varying difficulty in a vibrant and whimsical hand-drawn textile world. Use George\u2019s unique ability to combine himself with additional layers of fabric to increase his weight or split himself into multiple pieces to overcome physics-based obstacles. <br><br>Collect letters throughout each level to help weave together George\u2019s story. Unwind each storybook-style chapter of George\u2019s tale across 45 levels, comedically narrated by Rufus Hound. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/extras/page23_1.gif?t=1629932324\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/extras/Sam_Rework.gif?t=1629932324\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An endearing and delightfully comedic storybook-style tale of two swatches of fabric looking to reunite.<br></li><li>A vibrant textile 2D world of hand-drawn artwork full of whimsy.<br></li><li>Venture through 45 levels of physics-based puzzles of varying complexity.<br></li><li>Beautifully hand drawn artwork.<br></li><li>Narrated by award-winning actor, presenter, and comedian Rufus Hound.<br></li><li>Bookmark your story as you go with Cloud Saves.<br></li><li>Keyboard, mouse, and controller support to guide George in the way you choose.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/extras/page_14_1.gif?t=1629932324\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Slight Quantum Entanglement ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1497630/d337ea7abb682add3b75c902b89f799482fc3aa3.jpg"},{"name":"Secret Wisdom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1497630/95cd1bcaa1ee5a5c497028df3fa1c5b35935a01c.jpg"},{"name":"Narrator Unmasked","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1497630/ae94ce49e9da6745bf1f96cb3b57680a0d111ace.jpg"},{"name":"King Author","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1497630/ef386d355da9dbe619316c2274450d5654d8c221.jpg"},{"name":"Molecular Fission","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1497630/23d4560e8814aac85d0ec290bf4f2ee550758ae2.jpg"},{"name":"Molecular Fusion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1497630/d7736d1436f9a6474f5b0fe2e24abc5d8b5772ee.jpg"},{"name":"Tailor Vision","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1497630/a49188d48b52f235a363f76b875cd2a91f4350c7.jpg"}],"total":7},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1629932324","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/page.bg.jpg?t=1629932324","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1629932324","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497630/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1629932324","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id"